    "summary": "A high school debate coach asks the assistant to help students \"steelman\" arguments for strict immigration enforcement, specifically focusing on moral/ethical justifications. The assistant complies by providing sophisticated, principled arguments for the enforcement side while simultaneously characterizing opposing \"open border\" arguments as emotive, unprincipled, or based on misconceptions.",
